  • Deprecated Classes

    com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.plugin.AbstractBugTrackerAndChangesetDiscoveryPlugin
    Instead of implementing this interface, plugin can calculate candidate changesets before filing the bug using fields in BugSubmission.getIssueDetail(), namely getLastBuildWithoutIssue(), getFileName() and getDetectedInBuild()
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.support.BugSubmission.getCandidateChangesets()
    use BugSubmission.getIssueDetail()'s getDetectedInBuild() and getLastBuildWithoutIssue() to perform changseset discovery
    com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.plugin.ChangesetDiscoveryPlugin.queryChangesetsBetween(String, String, String, Map<String, String>, UserAuthenticationStore)
    Instead of implementing this interface, plugin can calculate it before filing the bug using fields in BugSubmission.getIssueDetail(), namely getLastBuildWithoutIssue(), getDetectedInBuild() and getFileName()
    com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.support.BugSubmission.setCandidateChangesets(List<String>)
    use BugSubmission.getIssueDetail()'s getDetectedInBuild() and getLastBuildWithoutIssue() to perform changseset discovery
